      "id": "lankar",
      "title": "Länkar",
      "body": "Förare tillhandahållen av Linköpings klätterklubb (http://linkopingsklatterklubb.se/index.php/forare.html).\n\nFörare av Västervik Climbing (http://www.vastervikclimbing.se/klattercentret/pdfer/).\n\n=In English="
    },
    {
      "id": "description",
      "title": "Description",
      "body": "One of Sweden's better sport crags offers slabby to slightly overhanging routes on solid red-tinted granite."
    },
    {
      "id": "directions",
      "title": "Directions",
      "body": "See map above. Turn right at the farm and park on the marked parking lot. The path to the crag has markings and starts by the barn. Please don't walk across farmland or the meadows."
    },
    {
      "id": "season",
      "title": "Season",
      "body": "The wall is east-facing and sunlit until 2PM. Best season is June-October."
    },
    {
      "id": "staying-there",
      "title": "Staying there",
      "body": "Risebo fritid ( http://www.risebofritid.se ) has cabins for rent. Överums vandrarhem (hostel) ( http://www.overum.nu ) is located 10 km from the crag. The closest supermarket is in Överum (13 km from the crag)."
    }
